data.value:
Business Inventory Systems is a database tool aimed towards the management of a furniture factory. This application manages inventory, procurement, sales, and employees, and offers insight into how well the company is performing in those aspects.
Using only the .NET framework and MySQL, as well as the connector for C# MySQL connections, the Business Inventory System is a clean, simple, and efficient solution for managing the everyday aspects of a manufacturing company of any caliber.
Developed by the hardworking and capable students at Team 13 Studio.
